B.i4=new A.dp("en","\ud83c\uddec\ud83c\udde7","English",B.Fc,"Figure 1: {name}. Drag back from the player to aim!","New game! Figure 1: {name}.","A pigeon has requisitioned your bat for the flock. It offered no receipt.","Your bat is now modeling Uncle Tolya's finest underpants. The jury is impressed.","You hit the kennel! Barbos is escorting you off the premises. (+1 penalty throw)",'CRASH! A window! Baba Zina: "MY GERANIUMS! I know your mother!" (+1 penalty throw)',"That window was already broken. Now it's just rude.","THUD. The building remains unimpressed.","SPLASH. A nearby cat looks at you with centuries of disappointment.","First blood! You now throw from the half-kon (6.5 m).","The letter stays sealed! Knock out the STAMP (center pin) first \u2014 the corners walked back.","That was the LAST one! Uncle Gena grabs the broom and sweeps you off the field! (+1 penalty throw)","The pigeon grows impatient with your tactical pause...","Direct hit! The pigeon leaves a one-star review. You run off to wash up.","Freshly washed and ready to continue.","Right on the cap! You clutch your head, squat... and crawl off the field with what dignity remains.","A quadcopter has intercepted your bat! Estimated delivery: 3\u20135 business days.","A mole! It surfaced right in the gorod and redecorated your figure. It seems proud.","Figure cleared! Next: {name} ({n}/15){letter}"," \u2014 kon only, stamp first!","All 15 figures! Total: {n} throws. Even Barbos looks impressed.","Throws","Half-kon \xb7 6.5 m","Pull back & release!","Figure","All 15 figures cleared!","Total throws:",'The pigeons rate your performance: "coo".',"Play again","Sound effects",'8-bit "Akh, Samara-gorodok"',"Evening falls... Level 2: the evening yard! The wind is up, and somebody parked IN the court.","A gust of wind! The bat now has opinions of its own.",'CRUNCH-tinkle! The car alarm wails! An angry profile fills a window: "MY LADA!!"',"The alarm again. The whole yard hums along by now.","The owner bursts out of the entrance in slippers and chases you off the field! (+1 penalty throw)",'A resident of the manhole surfaces and catches your bat mid-flight. "Mine now," he explains.',"POP! The streetlamp is out. The yard is now 20% more mysterious.","BOING! The hedgehog curls up; the bat ricochets. Nature is undefeated.","A bat (the animal) has claimed your bat (the stick). Confusing for everyone involved.","The bat hangs upside down nearby, eyeing your nap with interest...","SPLAT! The bat leaves a droppings-based review of your napping technique. You run off to wash up.","A spider is spinning a truly ambitious web between the two lamps.","Caught in the spider's web! It really committed to that thing.","Select level","Level 1 \u2014 Daytime yard","Level 2 \u2014 Evening yard","Level 3 \u2014 Winter yard","Snow has fallen! Level 3: winter gorodki. The wind is fierce (40%!), the mole is asleep, and the crow is watching.","WHUMP! An avalanche slides off the roof \u2014 only your head sticks out! Level lost. Winter wins this round.","The crow stole a gorodok, inspected it, and dropped it somewhere else. Utterly unapologetic.","The crow has claimed your bat. She has plans for it.","The crow eyes your nap with growing interest...","SPLAT! The crow expresses her opinion of sleeping players. You run off to wash up.","The bat is stuck in the yolka! The star wobbles disapprovingly.","The frozen puddle! The bat glides like it never learned to stop.",'A kid on a sled zooms by and carries your bat away. "MIIINE!"',B.EV,B.ET,B.EN)
